{"pageProps":{"metadata":{"title":"Notionについて","curriculumId":"19c2297f-7a72-8010-a6d2-c35d1f460328","category":"後期","visibility":["基礎班","発展班"],"tags":["基礎班","Notion","セットアップ"],"is_basic_curriculum":true,"id":"13"},"mdBlocks":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80f9-9935-eb117765daa5","parent":"ここでは、とても便利なメモツール **Notion** についてご紹介します。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-807e-aa81-c43b9dd8f3a2","parent":"Notionとは、**メモだけでなく、タスク管理、スケジュールの整理、授業ノートのまとめ、プロジェクト管理**など、さまざまなことがこれ一つでできる**万能ツール**です！","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8090-ba81-fe9d67bc5d8d","parent":"使いこなせば、これからの活動も大学生活も快適になること間違いナシです。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80d1-a666-e97f01a2cf63","parent":"ちなみに、基礎班のカリキュラムも**すべて**Notionで書いています。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8079-abd5-cc76d9209a03","parent":"以下では基本的な機能について解説します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80d4-be5f-d0ebff23badb","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80c6-bcac-e7ee4c748872","type":"child_page","parent":"## Notionとは","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8082-afb4-c9002214c5ce","type":"child_page","parent":"## 登録","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80d8-bf25-cc4e85fce8d7","type":"child_page","parent":"## ページとは","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-802a-9baa-ca7abdf16123","type":"child_page","parent":"## ブロックとは","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ac2297f-7a72-807d-88f0-e923ae2d0c9a","type":"child_page","parent":"## ブロックの使い方","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-800a-acad-ce5781498248","type":"child_page","parent":"## ページの共有（Web公開）","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8074-acf1-c25de8547d22","parent":"","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-800b-b569-f343425ae6ef","type":"heading_2","parent":"## 公式ドキュメントが豊富！","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80a4-97ff-d5f12c095fe2","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80ad-99b4-fd9d3fd944d8","parent":"Notionは公式のドキュメントがとても豊富で、基本的な使い方なら公式ドキュメントだけで事足ります。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-801b-9090-d3b4c4676de7","type":"bookmark","parent":"[bookmark](https://www.notion.so/ja/help/category/new-to-notion)","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-807d-9c42-d37d67be288f","parent":"Notionを使っていて、わからないこと・やりたいことが出てきたら、このカリキュラムはもちろん公式ドキュメントを参考にしてみるのもいいでしょう。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8077-98d8-d10eab2c88b9","parent":"また、Notionはかなりメジャーなツールなので、個人ブログやテック系記事でも頻繁に使い方が紹介されています。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-806e-80e6-fd80101ba379","parent":"Googleで検索するだけでかなりの情報が出てくるので、ガンガン活用しましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80ff-b1e8-fbf89a04322f","type":"heading_2","parent":"## 課題","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8069-8363-ca6b85f8be34","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8056-b845-d2cfb971f732","parent":"Notionの使い方にできるだけ慣れるために、課題を用意しました。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8068-8310-dd5b47ed6c4d","parent":"","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-8032-8865-da829d19e013","type":"child_page","parent":"## Notion課題","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-808d-85c7-cf7efa4e091e","parent":"","children":[]},{"blockId":"19c2297f-7a72-80c9-92c3-f29ac6aee649","type":"synced_block","parent":"","children":[]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"後期","id":"/posts/course/後期"},{"title":"Notionについて","id":"/posts/curriculums/19c2297f-7a72-8010-a6d2-c35d1f460328/19c2297f-7a72-8010-a6d2-c35d1f460328"}]},"__N_SSG":true}